<p>She wrote: 'It is what I miss the most about my current abilities or disabilities. Today, we managed to get it together to have a few minutes and I could not stop smiling.'</p>

<p>The Sweetest Thing actress revealed her MS diagnosis in October of 2018, and she's since documented her journey with the disease.</p>

